'''Vienna 整流器'''是[[脈衝寬度調變|脈衝寬度調變]]的[[整流器|整流器]]，可以接收[[三相交流電|三相交流電源]]，也是[[功率因數修正電路|功率因數修正電路]]，是Johann W. Kolar在1990年發明<ref>J. W. Kolar, „Dreiphasen-Dreipunkt-Pulsgleichrichter“, filed Dec. 23, 1993, File No.: AT2612/93, European Patent Appl.: EP 94 120 245.9-1242 entitled “Vorrichtung und Verfahren zur Umformung von Drehstrom in Gleichstrom”.</ref>。

==特點==
Vienna 整流器的特點如下：
* [[三相_(电学)|三相]]三電平的PWM[[整流器|整流器]]，其中包括三個功率晶體，可以控制輸出電壓<ref>J. W. Kolar, F. C. Zach, “A Novel Three-Phase Utility Interface Minimizing Line Current Harmonics of High-Power Telecommunications Rectifier Modules”, Record of the 16th IEEE International Telecommunications Energy Conference, Vancouver, Canada, Oct. 30 - Nov. 3, pp. 367-374 (1994) {{doi|10.1109/INTLEC.1994.396642}}.</ref>。
* 輸入只需要三條電源線，不需要連接對應中性點的線
* 主迴路維持[[欧姆定律|電阻]]特性{{Citation needed|date=2020年8月}}
* 升壓式架構（輸入電流連續）
* 單向的功率流動<ref name="KEZ96">J. W. Kolar, H. Ertl, F. C. Zach, “Design and Experimental Investigation of a Three-Phase High Power Density High Efficiency Unity Power Factor PWM (Vienna) Rectifier Employing a Novel Integrated Power Semiconductor Module”, Proceedings of the 11th IEEE Applied Power Electronics Conference, San Jose (CA), USA, March 3–7, Vol.2, pp.514-523 (1996) {{doi|10.1109/APEC.1996.500491}}.</ref>
* 高功率密度
* 低的導通共模EMI雜訊
* 要控制使中性點電壓穩定，比較簡單<ref>J. W. Kolar, U. Drofenik, F. C. Zach, “Space Vector Based Analysis of the Variation and Control of the Neutral Point Potential of Hysteresis Current Controlled Three-Phase/Switch/Level PWM Rectifier Systems”, Proceedings of the International Conference on Power Electronics and Drive Systems, Singapore, Feb.21-24, Vol.1, pp.22-33 (1995) {{doi|10.1109/PEDS.1995.404952}}.</ref>
* 低複雜度，實現成本低<ref name="KEZ96" />
* 低導通損失<ref>*Report “How to Design a 10kW Three-Phase AC/DC Interface Step by Step” at [http://www.gecko-research.com/reports/FrontEndComparison_Part_1.html www.gecko-research.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gecko-research.com/reports/FrontEndComparison_Part_1.html |date=20150114010328 }}</ref>
* 在電源三相不平衡，或是電源失效時，仍有可靠的行為特性（保證有類似電阻的特性）<ref>J. W. Kolar, U. Drofenik, F. C. Zach, “Current Handling Capability of the Neutral Point of a Three-Phase/Switch/Level Boost-Type PWM (Vienna) Rectifier”, Proceedings of the 27th IEEE Power Electronics Specialists Conference, Baveno, Italy, June 24–27, Vol.II, pp.1329-1336 (1996) {{doi|10.1109/PESC.1996.548754}}.</ref>

==拓樸==
Vienna整流器是三相三電平的PWM整流器。可以視為是三相的[[二極體電橋|二極體電橋]]，配合整合式的升壓轉換器。

==應用==
[[Image:Vienna_rectifier_real.jpg|thumb]]
Vienna整流器可以用在任何有用六個開關的轉換器，希望產生弦波輸入電流以及可控電壓輸出的情形，而且能量不需回灌到電路的應用下。在整務上，若有足夠空間，可以證明額外硬體成本的合理性時，適合使用Vienna整流器。包括：
* 電信電源
* [[不间断电源|不间断电源]]
* 交流驅動器的交流輸入端
右圖有風冷10 kW Vienna整流器（載波頻率400 kHz），有弧弦波輸入電流以及可控輸出電壓。大小是250mm x 120mm x 40mm，功率密度是8.5 kW/dm<sup>3</sup>，總重2.1 kg <ref>S. D. Round, P. Karutz, M. L. Heldwein, J. W. Kolar, “Towards a 30 kW/liter, Three-Phase Unity Power Factor Rectifier”, Proceedings of the 4th Power Conversion Conference (PCC'07), Nagoya, Japan, April 2–5, CD-ROM, {{ISBN|1-4244-0844-X}}, (2007).</ref>。

